para_trans: To approve the revised structure of posts at the establishment of the Office of the Commissioner of Charities, State of Maharashtra, Mumbai and its subordinate offices.
Government Corrigendum No: - CHA-20196 / Q. No.36 / Q.1
Madam Kama Marg, Martyr Rajguru Chowk,
Reference: - Department of Law & Justice Government Decision No. CHA-2016 / Q. No.36 / Q.1, D. 20.12.2022

The revised structure of the posts at the establishment of the offices under the Office of the Commissioner of Charities, Maharashtra State, Mumbai B has been approved by the relevant Government Decision. The designation in the tables of "Annexure-A - Regular posts" and "Annexure-D - Permanent-Temporary Classification of Regular posts" in the said Government Decision should be read as "Director of Bal" instead of "Deputy Director (Sal)" in section A, No. 5.
R. This Government Correctional Sheet is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
